WEBVTT

00:00:07.608 --> 00:00:12.346
<i>Dearest Mamo,</i>
<i>Listen to this: Rei</i>
<i>is posing as a</i>

00:00:12.379 --> 00:00:15.749
<i>fortune teller so she</i>
<i>can find out Seiya</i>
<i>and my secrets! Can</i>

00:00:15.782 --> 00:00:17.084
<i>you believe her?!</i>

00:00:18.352 --> 00:00:22.189
<i>Huh? Who does my</i>
<i>heart belong to, you</i>
<i>ask? รท[{chuckling]</i>

00:00:22.222 --> 00:00:24.691
<i>You'll just have to</i>
<i>watch and find out!</i>

00:02:09.730 --> 00:02:14.101
Fighter Star Power
Make Up!

00:02:15.569 --> 00:02:16.670
<i>Seiya?!</i>

00:02:24.077 --> 00:02:28.849
<i>Duty or Friendship:</i>
<i>Conflict Between the</i>
<i>Sailor Guardians!</i>

00:02:28.882 --> 00:02:33.420
I guess Seiya, Yaten,
and Taiki chose not to
come to school today.

00:02:33.453 --> 00:02:36.023
It's fine! I'm sure
they'll show up
tomorrow!

00:02:36.056 --> 00:02:37.724
Do you really think
so?

00:02:37.758 --> 00:02:39.059
Eh-em!

00:02:39.860 --> 00:02:40.961
[sighing]

00:02:40.994 --> 00:02:42.029
Oh! You're Right!

00:02:42.062 --> 00:02:43.697
Yeah, don't worry!

00:02:45.599 --> 00:02:48.268
But can you believe
that the Three Lights
were actually girls

00:02:48.302 --> 00:02:51.405
this whole time?
There goes my shot at
a famous boyfriend!

00:02:51.438 --> 00:02:53.941
Yeah, but we're
still friends with
them. After all, it

00:02:53.974 --> 00:02:55.709
doesn't change who
they are, right?

00:02:55.742 --> 00:02:57.110
Eh--

00:02:57.144 --> 00:02:59.513
There are more
important things to
worry about here!

00:02:59.546 --> 00:03:00.314
[grunting]

00:03:00.347 --> 00:03:02.082
W-What?

00:03:02.115 --> 00:03:04.918
I assume they have a
good reason for
hiding their true

00:03:04.952 --> 00:03:07.888
identities. And
also for becoming
idols.

00:03:07.921 --> 00:03:11.458
It does make me
wonder why they came
here from outside the

00:03:11.491 --> 00:03:12.659
solar system.

00:03:13.727 --> 00:03:16.063
Usagi... What's
wrong?

00:03:17.431 --> 00:03:21.001
Well, I guess I'm
still in shock about
all of this.

00:03:21.034 --> 00:03:22.236
In shock?

00:03:23.504 --> 00:03:25.639
It felt like we were
starting to get along
with those three

00:03:25.672 --> 00:03:27.374
pretty well, but
in the end,

00:03:27.407 --> 00:03:29.610
we knew nothing
about each other.

00:03:30.210 --> 00:03:31.478
Yeah, you're
right.

00:03:31.512 --> 00:03:33.780
Well, we didn't
actually tell them
anything about

00:03:33.814 --> 00:03:35.249
our secrets,
either.

00:03:51.365 --> 00:03:52.432
<i>Bun-head!</i>

00:03:55.435 --> 00:03:56.370
I--

00:04:05.512 --> 00:04:06.480
Oh?

00:04:06.513 --> 00:04:09.016
Why are you sitting
alone in the dark?

00:04:15.856 --> 00:04:17.624
Seiya! Snap
out of it!

00:04:17.658 --> 00:04:18.392
Uh?

00:04:18.425 --> 00:04:21.061
Oh, uh, sorry. What
was that?

00:04:21.094 --> 00:04:24.431
Listen, now's not
the time to be zoning
out, okay?

00:04:24.464 --> 00:04:25.766
Did you forget?

00:04:30.838 --> 00:04:32.105
[exhaling]

00:04:33.106 --> 00:04:35.108
You remember our top
priority, don't
you?

00:04:35.142 --> 00:04:39.012
Yeah... it's to
find our princess.

00:04:39.046 --> 00:04:40.214
That's right.

00:04:42.249 --> 00:04:45.018
But the problem is
those five girls keep
showing up.

00:04:45.052 --> 00:04:47.221
Maybe its not a
problem.

00:04:48.956 --> 00:04:52.459
Every time they cause
a scene out there, it
draws Galaxia's

00:04:52.492 --> 00:04:54.995
attention further
away from us.

00:04:55.662 --> 00:04:57.231
That's a good
point.

00:04:58.565 --> 00:05:02.769
In fact, it would be
much better for us if
the battle between

00:05:02.803 --> 00:05:05.339
Sailor Moon and
Galaxia escalated.

00:05:05.372 --> 00:05:06.406
Thats enough!

00:05:10.577 --> 00:05:13.547
Those girls are
putting their lives
on the line in order

00:05:13.580 --> 00:05:14.882
to protect their
planet!

00:05:14.915 --> 00:05:18.552
And you guys intend
on using them?! You
should be ashamed!

00:05:20.687 --> 00:05:23.023
I see. So
that's it.

00:05:23.056 --> 00:05:23.991
[gasping]

00:05:25.092 --> 00:05:26.393
You're just mad
'cause you're
worried about that

00:05:26.426 --> 00:05:27.561
girl, aren't you?

00:05:27.594 --> 00:05:28.462
What?!

00:05:29.263 --> 00:05:31.064
Humph! Well, I'm
right, aren't I?

00:05:31.098 --> 00:05:32.566
Knock it off,
both of you.

00:05:32.599 --> 00:05:34.034
[grunting]

00:05:35.335 --> 00:05:38.138
Look, I know you're
getting so defensive
about Sailor Moon

00:05:38.172 --> 00:05:40.574
because you see too
much of our princess
in her.

00:05:40.607 --> 00:05:43.810
There is only one
princess for us, Seiya.

00:05:43.844 --> 00:05:46.046
Please remember that.

00:05:47.648 --> 00:05:48.348
Hm.

00:06:03.463 --> 00:06:07.234
I, Sailor Tin Nyanko,
along with Crow
here...

00:06:07.267 --> 00:06:08.535
Mm.

00:06:08.569 --> 00:06:11.071
... have agreed to
team up so that we
could hopefully be of

00:06:11.104 --> 00:06:14.908
greater use to you,
Master Galaxia.
Isn't that right?

00:06:14.942 --> 00:06:16.276
Excuse me?

00:06:17.344 --> 00:06:18.378
Mm.

00:06:19.446 --> 00:06:22.216
You do remember our
agreement, don't
you, Crow?

00:06:22.249 --> 00:06:23.183
Come on!

00:06:24.685 --> 00:06:27.221
No, wait! Please,
forgive me!

00:06:27.788 --> 00:06:29.156
That planet...

00:06:29.189 --> 00:06:29.857
Huh?

00:06:29.890 --> 00:06:30.557
Huh?

00:06:31.158 --> 00:06:33.727
<i>Oh, the solar system.</i>

