Huh? From that remote
planet? No way!

00:06:43.036 --> 00:06:47.808
I plan to conquer the
entire galaxy and no
one shall interfere.

00:06:47.841 --> 00:06:49.810
Oh, right. Yes of
course.

00:06:49.843 --> 00:06:53.380
I refuse to even
allow the existence
of those who oppose

00:06:53.413 --> 00:06:57.251
me. That entire
planet could die for
all I care.

00:06:57.284 --> 00:07:00.821
Hurry and bring me
every last Star Seed
you find there.

00:07:00.854 --> 00:07:02.623
There is not a
moment to lose.

00:07:03.857 --> 00:07:04.525
Hm.

00:07:04.558 --> 00:07:06.126
Just as you wish.

00:07:07.928 --> 00:07:08.929
[grunting]

00:07:08.962 --> 00:07:11.331
Ugh, how annoying!

00:07:11.365 --> 00:07:14.401
Just when I thought
this job couldn't
get any worse.

00:07:14.434 --> 00:07:17.838
And that Crow chick
doesn't seem too
useful either.

00:07:17.871 --> 00:07:19.339
The hell this?

00:07:20.741 --> 00:07:22.676
Once trash, always
trash.

00:07:25.279 --> 00:07:27.447
Excuse me, what are
you doing?

00:07:27.481 --> 00:07:30.884
Oh look, Trash Part
2. Can't you tell?

00:07:30.918 --> 00:07:32.653
I'm getting rid
of garbage.

00:07:32.686 --> 00:07:34.054
What? How dare you?!

00:07:34.087 --> 00:07:37.457
Siren took her job
seriously until her
last breath!

00:07:37.491 --> 00:07:38.525
Yeah, right.

00:07:39.793 --> 00:07:41.962
Master Galaxia killed
her off because she
was a loser who

00:07:41.995 --> 00:07:44.831
couldn't complete
the task she was
assigned.

00:07:44.865 --> 00:07:46.033
[grunting]

00:07:47.134 --> 00:07:49.336
<i>If you're not</i>
<i>careful, then</i>
<i>it's likely</i>

00:07:49.369 --> 00:07:51.138
<i>you'll end up the</i>
<i>same way.</i>

00:07:52.406 --> 00:07:54.174
Just shut up!

00:07:55.676 --> 00:07:59.613
Listen... No need to
get worked up.

00:08:02.749 --> 00:08:06.486
You'll see. I'm
going to prove you
wrong about Siren.

00:08:08.388 --> 00:08:11.291
Yep, she's gonna be
as useless as I
thought.

