If someone from
school sees me
like this,

00:08:31.011 --> 00:08:32.613
then my life
is over.

00:08:32.646 --> 00:08:33.881
<i>Um...</i>

00:08:33.914 --> 00:08:35.115
You open?

00:08:35.649 --> 00:08:37.584
O-Oh! Come in.

00:08:40.087 --> 00:08:42.089
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>Wow, he's pretty</i>
<i>cute.</i>

00:08:44.691 --> 00:08:48.595
<i>Seiya?! Of course I</i>
<i>see someone I know</i>
<i>right away.</i>

00:08:52.232 --> 00:08:55.936
You see, I keep
thinking about
this girl.

00:08:55.969 --> 00:08:58.772
<i>Could he be talking</i>
<i>about Usagi?!</i>

00:08:58.805 --> 00:09:02.876
One who I've
actually been lying
to for some time now.

00:09:02.910 --> 00:09:05.078
I was going to tell
her the truth,

00:09:05.112 --> 00:09:07.781
but she found out
before I had a
chance to.

00:09:07.814 --> 00:09:12.152
<i>What do I do? He's</i>
<i>confessing things I</i>
<i>can't help him with!</i>

00:09:12.186 --> 00:09:14.888
It's obvious my
friends aren't
happy about me being

00:09:14.922 --> 00:09:17.424
distracted by how I
feel about all this.

00:09:17.457 --> 00:09:20.594
But it's not like I
don't already know
that this isn't the

00:09:20.627 --> 00:09:22.262
time to get
sidetracked.

00:09:23.764 --> 00:09:27.534
And besides... She
may not even decide
to forgive me for

00:09:27.568 --> 00:09:29.236
lying to her.

00:09:29.269 --> 00:09:31.939
But all I wanna do is
see her again!

00:09:31.972 --> 00:09:34.741
I just... don't know
what to do anymore.

00:09:40.814 --> 00:09:43.317
[chuckling]
I'm an idiot.

00:09:43.350 --> 00:09:46.520
Seeking out an
answer from some
fortune teller.

00:09:48.021 --> 00:09:49.857
Well... sorry.

00:09:49.890 --> 00:09:50.624
Wait!

00:09:51.758 --> 00:09:54.728
<i>Crap. But I can't</i>
<i>let him leave like</i>
<i>this.</i>

00:09:55.929 --> 00:09:58.332
If you could please
sit back down, sir.

00:10:00.734 --> 00:10:03.070
<i>Great. Now what</i>
<i>do I do?</i>

00:10:04.338 --> 00:10:07.441
<i>It wouldn't be a</i>
<i>problem, if I had an</i>
<i>answer for this.</i>

00:10:11.712 --> 00:10:13.146
Do you see something?

00:10:16.517 --> 00:10:18.652
The answer
that you seek.

00:10:18.685 --> 00:10:19.486
[gasping]

00:10:23.590 --> 00:10:25.058
It's--

00:10:26.994 --> 00:10:27.761
Unclear.

00:10:27.794 --> 00:10:28.529
[grunting]

00:10:30.130 --> 00:10:32.833
It's important that
you be sincere.

00:10:32.866 --> 00:10:36.470
If you truly feel bad
about lying, then go
apologize to this

00:10:36.503 --> 00:10:39.606
girl. I think
that's a good place
for you to start.

00:10:41.608 --> 00:10:42.676
Ya know...

00:10:42.709 --> 00:10:43.443
Hm?

00:10:45.345 --> 00:10:47.481
You got a pretty keen
eye there.

00:10:47.514 --> 00:10:50.384
It was silly of me to
go straight to a
fortune teller

00:10:50.417 --> 00:10:52.953
instead of just doing
what needed to be
done.

00:10:52.986 --> 00:10:56.523
But I'm glad that I
did, 'cause you helped
me see the light.

00:10:57.024 --> 00:10:58.425
So Thank you.

00:11:03.363 --> 00:11:08.435
I almost had a heart
attack. Can I go
home yet?!

00:11:08.468 --> 00:11:09.536
[panicking]

00:11:09.570 --> 00:11:10.737
C-Come in.

00:11:12.873 --> 00:11:14.675
<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>[gasping] Usagi?!</i>

00:11:16.310 --> 00:11:20.447
Uh--There's this
boy that I've been
thinking a lot about.

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:21.481
Huh?!

00:11:22.149 --> 00:11:24.718
(thinking)
Uh-oh.

00:11:24.751 --> 00:11:26.086
[clearing throat]

00:11:26.119 --> 00:11:30.390
I'm sensing that
you have a boyfriend
already, don't you?

00:11:30.424 --> 00:11:34.228
Yeah, I do. But the
boy I'm talking
about isn't someone

00:11:34.261 --> 00:11:35.762
who I'm in love
with.

00:11:35.796 --> 00:11:38.565
[sighing]
Well, that's
a relief.

00:11:38.599 --> 00:11:39.433
Huh?

00:11:39.466 --> 00:11:40.701
Uh, go on.

