You're better at
taking action than
you are at thinking,

00:11:52.813 --> 00:11:56.617
right? So just do the
first thing that
comes to your mind.

00:11:57.351 --> 00:11:58.252
How did--

00:11:59.286 --> 00:12:00.487
[groaning]

00:12:00.521 --> 00:12:03.223
If he's not at
school, then
go to him.

00:12:03.257 --> 00:12:06.527
But... I don't even
know where he is
right now.

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:08.295
Find him.

00:12:10.330 --> 00:12:11.298
[sighing]

