You're worried that
he might reject you
or refuse to talk to

00:12:19.239 --> 00:12:21.675
you. But if you're
afraid and keep
running away,

00:12:21.708 --> 00:12:25.412
you'll only end up
losing what's
really important!

00:12:25.445 --> 00:12:28.615
You're good. How
is it you know so
much about me?!

00:12:28.649 --> 00:12:30.984
It's easy when
you've know someone
as long as I've

00:12:31.018 --> 00:12:33.654
known you at this
point. Duh.

00:12:33.687 --> 00:12:35.422
[gasping]
It's you, Rei?!

00:12:35.455 --> 00:12:38.225
All that matters is
having the courage to
do what needs to be

00:12:38.258 --> 00:12:41.395
done. You can dwell
on what he thinks
after you go see him

00:12:41.428 --> 00:12:43.363
and tell him what's
been on your mind.

00:12:43.397 --> 00:12:46.233
The Usagi Tsukino I
know would stand tall
and face her

00:12:46.266 --> 00:12:48.168
problems,
no matter what!

00:12:49.770 --> 00:12:50.637
Here!

00:12:50.671 --> 00:12:51.405
Uh!

00:12:52.072 --> 00:12:54.441
[gasping]
Wait, this is--

