<i>This is Jack's</i>
<i>Evening Guest where I</i>
<i>read your letters and</i>

00:13:23.570 --> 00:13:24.671
<i>play requests.</i>

00:13:24.705 --> 00:13:27.074
Joining me here
tonight are the
members of teen idol

00:13:27.107 --> 00:13:28.742
group, the Three
Lights.

00:13:28.775 --> 00:13:31.645
Thanks to you guys,
we seem to have a lot
of women in our

00:13:31.678 --> 00:13:32.946
studio audience.

00:13:32.980 --> 00:13:35.549
<i>I'm told the number</i>
<i>of people buying</i>
<i>tickets to attend</i>

00:13:35.582 --> 00:13:39.486
<i>tonight's show</i>
<i>skyrocketed, due to</i>
<i>your popularity.</i>

00:13:39.520 --> 00:13:43.056
<i>Now, why don't you</i>
<i>pick a postcard and</i>
<i>song request from our</i>

00:13:43.090 --> 00:13:44.358
<i>listeners, Seiya?</i>

00:13:45.459 --> 00:13:47.127
<i>Uh... hello?</i>

00:13:47.561 --> 00:13:48.262
Seiya!

00:13:48.295 --> 00:13:49.830
Yes?

00:13:49.863 --> 00:13:52.032
How about you pick a
postcard now?

00:13:52.566 --> 00:13:53.433
<i>Sure.</i>

00:14:00.140 --> 00:14:03.944
Hm. We've gotta
start again from
somewhere, right?

00:14:03.977 --> 00:14:08.248
Okay. Can you please
play the song, "To
the Shooting Star"?

00:14:08.282 --> 00:14:08.882
Hm?!

00:14:08.916 --> 00:14:11.018
This one's
from Starlight.

00:14:11.051 --> 00:14:13.053
I don't remember
that postcard.

