<i>(thinking)</i>
<i>Seiya, I'm</i>
<i>sorry, too.</i>

00:15:08.742 --> 00:15:13.380
<i>I never tried to</i>
<i>understand who you</i>
<i>really were.</i>

00:15:13.413 --> 00:15:17.851
<i>But now I want to</i>
<i>know. So, I'll be</i>
<i>here, ready to tell</i>

00:15:17.885 --> 00:15:20.120
<i>the truth when you</i>
<i>are, too.</i>

