Here.

00:15:28.362 --> 00:15:29.463
Thanks!

00:15:29.496 --> 00:15:31.331
[chatting]

00:15:35.836 --> 00:15:38.372
Thanks so much for
coming today.

00:15:38.405 --> 00:15:44.244
No, thank you.
Because, I mean, you
know, that message.

00:15:44.945 --> 00:15:46.113
Uh--

00:15:48.115 --> 00:15:50.284
Maybe... not now.

00:15:51.318 --> 00:15:54.788
But someday, we will
understand.

